## 🚀 Performance-Driven Design

### 1. Perceived Performance (Feels Fast ≠ Is Fast)

**Optimistic UI Updates:**
```tsx
const handleLike = async () => {
  // Update UI immediately (optimistic)
  setLiked(true);
  setLikeCount(prev => prev + 1);

  try {
    // Then sync with server
    await api.likePost(postId);
  } catch (error) {
    // Rollback on error
    setLiked(false);
    setLikeCount(prev => prev - 1);
    toast.error('Failed to like post');
  }
};
```

**Skeleton Screens (Better than Spinners):**
```tsx
{loading ? (
  <div className="space-y-4 animate-pulse">
    <div className="h-12 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded" />
    <div className="h-32 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded" />
  </div>
) : (
  <Content />
)}
```

**Progress Indication:**
```tsx
// Bad: Indeterminate spinner (feels slow)
<Spinner />

// Good: Percentage (feels faster, even if same duration)
<div className="text-center">
  <div className="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta-700">{progress}%</div>
  <div className="mt-2 h-2 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
    <div
      className="h-full bg-gradient-button-primary transition-all duration-500"
      style={{ width: `${progress}%` }}
    />
  </div>
  <p className="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Uploading...</p>
</div>
```

### 2. Design for Performance Budgets

**Neuman Brain Constraints:**
- Bundle: < 200KB gzipped
- Images: < 100KB per image
- Total page weight: < 500KB

**Design Decisions:**

**Use SVG Icons (Scalable, Tiny):**
```tsx
✅ GOOD: SVG icons (2KB for entire icon set)
import { Plus, Edit, Trash } from 'lucide-react';

❌ BAD: Icon fonts (50KB+ for full set)
<i className="fas fa-plus"></i>
```

**Lazy Load Images:**
```tsx
<img
  src={thumbnail}
  loading="lazy"
  decoding="async"
  alt="Task preview"
/>
```

**Prioritize Critical CSS:**
```tsx
// Inline critical CSS in <head>
// Load full CSS async
<link rel="preload" href="/style.css" as="style" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" media="print" onload="this.media='all'" />
```

### 3. Animation Performance (60fps Non-Negotiable)

**GPU-Accelerated Properties Only:**
```css
/* ✅ FAST - GPU accelerated */
transform: translateY(-4px);
opacity: 0.5;
filter: blur(10px);

/* ❌ SLOW - Triggers layout/paint */
margin-top: -4px;
width: 100px;
background-color: red;
```

**Force GPU Acceleration:**
```css
.animated {
  transform: translateZ(0); /* Force GPU layer */
  will-change: transform, opacity; /* Hint to browser (use sparingly) */
}
```

**Remove `will-change` After Animation:**
```tsx
const [isHovered, setIsHovered] = useState(false);

<div
  onMouseEnter={() => setIsHovered(true)}
  onMouseLeave={() => setIsHovered(false)}
  style={{ willChange: isHovered ? 'transform' : 'auto' }}
>
  Content
</div>
